  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink279-kilavi">iravukkuṟi vēṇṭum talaimakaṉait tōḻi varav arumai kūṟi maṟuttatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
         
What the confidante said, refusing the hero who desired a night tryst, speaking of the difficulty of the [heroine’s] coming [to the tryst].
                 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink279">
<l>kalliva riṟṟi pulluvaṉa vēṟik</l>
<l>kuḷavi mēynta manti tuṇaiyoṭu</l>
<l>varaimicai yukaḷu nāṭa nīvariṟ</l>
<l>kallakat tatuvem mūrē</l>
<l>yampaṟ cēri yalarāṅ kaṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where female monkeys,</l>
        <l>having grazed on wild jasmine,</l>
        <l>embrace and climb the Talbot fig tree</l>
        <l>[whose roots] spread across the stones,</l>
        <l>leap to the mountain top</l>
        <l>with [their] companions—</l>
        <l rend="space">if you come,</l>
        <l rend="space">our village, with stones within,</l>
        <l>our quarter, [teeming with] calumny,</l>
        <l>will become a place of gossip.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
